"                ນີ້ແມ່ນ\n"
"                <t t-if=\"object.name\">\n"
"                    ໃບຫຼຸດໜີ້ທີ່ອອກດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ <span style=\"font-weight:bold;\" t-"
"out=\"object.name or ''\">RINV/2021/05/0001</span>\n"
"                </t>\n"
"                <t t-else=\"\">\n"
"                    ໃບຫຼຸດໜີ້ທີ່ອອກດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ\n"
"                </t>\n"
"                <t t-if=\"object.invoice_origin\">\n"
"                    (ອ້າງອີງ: <t t-out=\"object.invoice_origin or ''\">SUB003</"
